snippet.title: Enchanted Tales of Beauty and the Beast Now Open; Barbarians; Amber Heard; D23 Expo Delayed to 2022
snippet.description: D23 Expo 2022; Enchanted Tales of Beauty and the Beast now open at Disneyland Tokyo; live-action Beauty and the Beast-themed dark ride in development for Magic Kingdom of WDW; Disney+ to debut singalong songs; Amber Heard to return as Mira in the DCEU film series; Netflix's Barbarians launches recent trailer and its starring Naomi Scott; Raptor Escape announcement trailer; PS5 to include external and internal backup storages like Xbox Series X aka Xbox 4K.
